window.bookSummaryJSON = "Following on from the brilliant <i>The No. 1 Ladies' Detective Agency</i>, <i>Tears of the Giraffe</i> charts the further adventures of Mma Ramotswe, Botswana's only female private detective. It's going to take all her intuition and eminent sensibility for Mma Ramotswe to crack her hardest case yet: the decade-old disappearance of an American on the edge of the Kalahari."; 
